milestones.description: David Gower and Allan Lamb's 159-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 153 between Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards
David Gower and Allan Lamb's 159-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 108 between Graham Gooch and Mike Brearley
Madan Lal and Kapil Dev's 65-run partnership is IND's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Syed Kirmani and Kapil Dev
